Probably Austroasiatic ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Compare:
* Tai-Kadai: {{cog|tai-pro|*pitᴰ||duck}} > {{cog|th|เป็ด}}, {{cog|lo|ເປັດ}}, {{cog|za|bit}};
* Austroasiatic: {{cog|mkh-vie-pro|*viːt||duck}} > {{cog|vi|vịt}};
* Sino-Tibetan:
** {{cog|mxj|kɹɑi³⁵ pit⁵⁵|kɹɑi³⁵ '''pit⁵⁵'''|duck}};
** {{cog|bxd|pjɛ̱t⁵⁵||duck}}, {{cog|atb|pje̱t⁵⁵||duck}};
** Proto-Lolo-Burmese ''*baj¹/²'' (“duck”) > {{cog|my|ဘဲ}}.

