# {{†}} [[duck]]
#* {{zh-x|凡 摯，天子 鬯，諸侯 圭，卿 羔，大夫 雁，士 雉，庶人 之 摯 '''@匹'''；童子 委 摯 而 退。|By way of presents of introduction, the son of Heaven uses spirits of black millet; feudal princes, their symbols of jade; a high minister, a lamb; a Great officer, a goose; an (ordinary) officer, a pheasant; a common man, a '''duck'''. Lads should bring their article, and withdraw.|ref=Liji}}
